  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study aims to determine the effect size of magnesium and bicarbonate supplementation as a
      basis for future randomized controlled trials aiming at the T50-guided improvement of hard
      clinical endpoints in dialysis patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
